        <Parent_String>pottery glazing (process or technique) [300195111], pottery decorating techniques [300053909], pottery techniques [300053901], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
